<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="C" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Crisp" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Crisp,</orth> curled: <cit><quote>leave your c. channels,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tmp 4.130" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. IV, 130</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>the Severn . . . hid his c. head,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 1.3.106" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A I, 3, 106</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>c. heaven,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tim 4.3.183" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. IV, 3, 183</bibl></cit> (so called from the curled clouds).
